# Tweakpane texture status rows

Follow **`Docs/tweakpane-texture-status-instruction-concise.md`** (full detail: `Docs/tweakpane-texture-status-instruction.md`).

Mask-dependent main-config effects use **`mask-status`** groups (`createMaskStatusSchemaGroup` / `createMaskStatusSchemaGroups`), not `textureStatus` strings. Rows sit under **Enabled**: label **`Texture`** (one mask) or **suffix** (multi, A→Z); chip uses `formatTextureStatusMessage`; square **`?`** for setup help. Probe via `resolvePopulatedMaskStatus` (runtime after populate only); `refreshEffectMaskStatus(effectId)` after populate and on Enabled toggle. Missing = `No _Suffix Texture Found` (grey disabled / red enabled). Migrated: Water/Bush/Tree/Iridescence/Prism/Fluid; Specular; Window Light; Painted/Building shadows; Camera Grade (`colorCorrection` / `_Outdoors`); Fire/Ash/Dust; Water Splashes + Bubbles.
